high_descs: Cross the kitchen to stand in front of the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the white coffee mug from the counter.
Carry the mug to the refrigerator.
Open the fridge, place the mug on the top shelf, close the fridge, and then remove the mug once chilled.
Carry the mug back to the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the mug on the base of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled mug to the coffee maker.
